{"tid":1550816,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"撤銷中國大學生的簽證","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:55:17.000Z","uid":290949,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1652a7bfdf8ec2b3df6b46f30a6dbfa3ebe8099f","tid":1550816,"uid":290949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"撤銷中國大學生的簽證，這些簽證擾亂了本來和平的親香港抗議活動<br />\nRevoke the visas of Chinese college students who disrupted the otherwise peaceful pro-Hong Kong protests<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frevoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC6arsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=601c85f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests</a><br />\nDeadline : 2019-9-19"},{"pid":"6043d5bef9770dd02e4d7438ea72ad59bc94af56","tid":1550816,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c6290bb1ba4f6fc6318b2557e26bc0f55043161","tid":1550816,"uid":110331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:54:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">We may have lost a battle but NOT the war<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地今日機場喺輸左但場運動未</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日美領大遊行要齊人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要過左五大訴求就會成真！<br />\n政府要係2020實行真。普選立法會<br />\n侵犯人權的官員人和家庭成員簽證可被撤銷，外資可被凍結！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmfHUdC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmfHUdC.png&h=89bc45e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksEYsyD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FksEYsyD.png&h=ab62bc0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">呢個先喺真真正正嘅END GAME<br />\n未清楚咩事可以睇下面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">草案要求中國政府履行承諾，容許港人治港、高度自治，並且確保香港人可以通過普選，選出行政長官及立法會所有議席，當中特別設下「時限」，要求在2020年普選立法會。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2。</span></span></span><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">特別警告香港若就23條立法，除非可證明不影響港人及外籍居民的人權，否則美國政府可中止《香港政策法》等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">3。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">侵犯人權的及損害香港自治的官員及人士的清單。名單裡的人在美國的資產可被凍結、個人和家庭成員的簽證可被撤銷，要求美國總統調查及制裁打壓香港自由的官員。會交代香港是否有官員因協助侵犯人權而需要受制裁。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">這有助國際社會持續監察香港的狀況，如能每年通過查證，實際上等同美國年年為一國兩制投下信任一票，這一方面有助有助保障香港高度自治，同時亦會加強國際社會對香港的信心。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DYm9M6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DYm9M6.png&h=40ab8a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LehviFs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLehviFs.png&h=cadff255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">未簽聯署即做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC6arsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=00ec65af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日12點遮打花園見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7A6LR0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7A6LR0y.png&h=81aa1e4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62f2b2d1eb86b28c7cd6422f1cb05c020812f3f4","tid":1550816,"uid":319698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T